TRIVIA:
1.  The film runs on the premise that the old MK-ULTRA program of the CIA which studied mind control and chemical interrogation techniques is still running.  The original program was supposedly shut down in 1973, but rumors continue to abound that the program or some form of the original MK-ULTRA program has continued to run into present day.


